entry.title: jenkinsci/ecu-test-execution-plugin
entry.summary: This plugin enables a platform-independent test execution. Due to the reduced complexity and communication via REST API, it provides an easy and reliable entry into continuous testing. It integrates ECU-TEST with Jenkins and allows report generation and its upload of automated test execution.
